    "claudeCode": "Helper-guided env-first path through ~/.claude/settings.json. The checked env contract is ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://payg.nodenetwork.ovh/v1 plus ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=<nodeclaw_access_key>.",
    "geminiCli": "Helper-guided env-first path. Set GOOGLE_GEMINI_BASE_URL=https://payg.nodenetwork.ovh and GEMINI_API_KEY=<nodeclaw_access_key>; the effective Google / Gemini-shaped route family still resolves under v1beta.",
    "hermes": "Helper-guided profile-local path. Create or update a dedicated Hermes profile under ~/.hermes/profiles/<profile> with profile-local .env, config.yaml, and SOUL.md, then point the main model route at the NodeClaw custom endpoint via the profile env/config contract."
